spell_list.description: The troubador's impairments that affect encounters will siphon a portion of what they impair back to the troubador's group. Mitigation impairments will grant the group a triggered effect instead of mitigation.
spell_list.description_pvp: The troubador's impairments that affect encounters will siphon a portion of what they impair back to the troubador's group. Mitigation impairments will grant the group a triggered effect instead of mitigation.

effect_list.description: Demoralizing Processional will increase the group's attributes and skills.
Chaos Anthem will increase the group's wisdom and restore health slowly over time.
Zander's Choral Rebuff will grant a triggered damage effect that applies on spell attacks.
Disheartening Descant will increase the group's strength and agility.
